text:

trans:
[redacted_name] posed a question to Mr. Yu in her sweet, charming voice. At that moment, my gaze lingered on [redacted_name]’s full breasts, faintly revealed under her white uniform—
[redacted_name]’s shapely, soft, and ample breasts. I just want to touch it! I want to caress them! I want to fondle them!!! I really, really, really, really want to—so badly!!!
“[redacted_name], can I touch your breasts?”
